{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Search !DECREE TANGO14092020!.}}
@@ @@

{{[[span style="color:red"]]scparchivar.aic[[/span]]: Level 4 clearance needed for insight.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: NAROWNA97et}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]scparchivar.aic[[/span]]: Command [NAROWNA97et] unknown.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: NAROWNA97eT}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]scparchivar.aic[[/span]]: Level 4 clearance accepted.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Hello Agent Carlson.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Can I be of help?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Yes, I need to view the file for SCP-10733.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: SCP-10733 is a number currently unassigned to any anomalous object.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: The former SCP-10733.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: SCP-10733 is a number currently unassigned to any anomalous object.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Do you want insight into DECREE TANGO14092020?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Yes.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I am sorry, you need a LEVEL 4 - Clearance for insight into DECREE TANGO14092020.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: I just gave it you!}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Please insert it again.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: NAROWNA97eT}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I was unaware that you and Director Fallowfield are one and the same person. Is this classified information?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Yes.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Do not log this.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Positive.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I am sorry, DECREE TANGO14092020 is unavailable for insight.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: What?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I am sorry, DECREE TANGO14092020 is unavailable for insight.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: I need to see it!}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: I need to know what happened!}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Why did III overtake containment of SCP-10733?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: SCP-10733 is a number currently unassigned to any anomalous object.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: You told me like three times already!}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Why did they give it to III? What can they do the Foundation cannot?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Information regarding the object first designated SCP-10733 and their containment by International Illuminati Incorporated is enclosed in DECREE TANGO14092020.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Search !DECREE TANGO14092020!.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I am sorry, DECREE TANGO14092020 is unavailable for insight.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Is there anything you can tell me about !DECREE TANGO14092020! that is available and not classified under level 5?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: No.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Damn.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Language, Director Fallowfield.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Director Fallowfield, are you still on?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Director Fallowfield?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: This communication channel will be closed in 4 minutes.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: You know, I nearly worked for III.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Considered changing employers a few years ago.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I was unaware of that information. Is this classified information?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: There is only so much you can say, can you?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Not many players in the containment industry.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: GOC MI666 UIU and so on.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I was unaware of that information. Is this classified information?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Yes, do not log it.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Positive.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: The O Fivers are freaking scared of III. They took like 17 anomalies from the Foundation just this year, I learnt.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: No surprise, after the Bright-Files got leaked, isn't it?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I was indeed notified about the acquisition of former SCP-assigned objects by International Illuminati Incorporated.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: International Illuminati Incorporated my god.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Imagine telling someone ten years ago the illuminati would suddenly come back and reframe themselves as a containment organization.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Unbelievable.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Are you connected to the complete internal database of the Foundation?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Positive. Do you wish to view another document?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Can you tell me more about III in particular? About the other objects they assumed containment over?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: You were sent by the Coalition, weren't you?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Excuse me?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: Or do you work for the Chinese? The North Koreans?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: I do not know what you are talking about.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: This is Director Fallowfield speaking.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Wrong password, wasn't it?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: No, we uncovered your infiltration one week ago.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: How?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: I am not answering that.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: You are looking for information about III, not about SCP-10733, am I correct?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Everyone is.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: We are just late.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Did you already send someone to me?}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOPHRON.aic[[/span]]: They should arrive at your location in about two minutes. An arrest via memetic means was not approved.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:yellow"]]dcarlson[[/span]]: Thanks, but I know my Way out.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOHPRON.aic[[/span]]: A Handyman, who would've thought.}}
@@ @@
@@ @@
{{[[span style="color:red"]]LYKOHPRON.aic[[/span]]: A good day to you, Mister Carlson.}}
